{"tid":2382005,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際律師會曾轟國安法 鄭若驊退出","createTime":"2021-01-27T04:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T04:29:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ff764a0c0befa8127893f791d01649d64fa772","tid":2382005,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:07:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/HQGKAYBDWZEEZGJWLV7M4UMKEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FHQGKAYBDWZEEZGJWLV7M4UMKEE%2F&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn6e24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=b1f976c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FHQGKAYBDWZEEZGJWLV7M4UMKEE%2F&h=d9baab88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/HQGKAYBDWZEEZGJWLV7M4UMKEE/</a><br />\n<br />\n國際律師會曾轟國安法 鄭若驊退出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4hkG6IppKYgXfyalJIulQUMMecU=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P4XP44ATVVAT7IAQEXTHWKPW7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4hkG6IppKYgXfyalJIulQUMMecU%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP4XP44ATVVAT7IAQEXTHWKPW7M.jpg&h=21e48700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭若驊本月在行會利益申報刪去國際律師協會成員身份。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法惹國際關注，部份涉事官員甚至被制裁，行政會議成員個人利益登記冊資料顯示，律政司長鄭若驊本月11日刪去國際律師協會成員，等同退會。有關協會自港版國安法出台後，多次為香港人權發聲；本報正向律政司查詢鄭若驊退會理由。<br />\n<br />\n國際律師協會早在去年國安法生效後，已發聲明指國安法違背法治及中國對港基本政策，促當局停止執行並諮詢港人。協會近月亦曾譴責警方大規模拘捕逾50名民主派，質疑大搜捕法律理據、促請中方尊重言論自由、人權及法治；同時亦關注12港人案審訊情況，以及代理律師被威脅吊銷執照；翻查有關聲明在鄭若驊申請退會後發出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或因制裁無法交會費<br />\n<br />\n國際律師協會昨晚回覆本報查詢時稱，該會屬於志願組織，會員來自全球170個國家，會員有權決定是否公開其會員身份，該會不會討論個別會員身份。<span class=\"orange\">據協會資料，會員每年可透過信用卡、銀行滙款或支票付款續交會費，由於鄭若驊受美國制裁，未知是否因為銀行服務受影響而無法以相關方法付款而退會。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，特首林鄭月娥也在昨天於利益申報刪走香港大學建築學院建築文物保護課程學名譽教授一項，意味退回教授名銜，本報亦正就此向特首辦查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3717edfa75602a38f720bcf24e173513ad97dc98","tid":2382005,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"反而呢啲學位同名銜都係形同虛設<br />\n成班都冇腦嘅<br />\n要嚟把撚<br />\n<br />\n叫中共CUP隻豬仔畀佢哋算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740a119152c76237866169a7870fa571cde43195","tid":2382005,"uid":316927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"777 建築文物保護名譽教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad85c8ede8d90ccc9b6e870f79815294313ffea2","tid":2382005,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:29:14.000Z","msg":"搞單邊主義<br />\n死硬<br />\n<br />\n維尼講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}